    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan, with minimum quality checks documented for each. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) provides a conservative safety margin. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
